The CHIP editorial says:
The “Free YouTube to FLVConverter” downloads YouTube videos quickly and in good quality and then converts them – not just to FLV.

Free YouTube to FLV Converter
Free YouTube to FLV Converter
It was never faster to download YouTube videos and convert them to the most popular video and audio formats. To start the process, just copy the URL of a video to the program, click on “Download” and the “Free YouTube to FLV Converter” will start downloading.

If you want to convert the video directly to one of the most popular video and audio formats, just click on “Convert” and select the file format.

If you want to play after converting on your laptop or PC the videos, we recommend the popular VLC media player .

New in this update is the support of the new YouTube Playlists.

Conclusion: The tool provides cool features and does his work in excellent speed. Unfortunately, the “Free YouTube to FLV Converter” tries to install unnecessary additional programs during the installation. We recommend that you refuse all offers.
